briefTitle: Enhancing Exercise in Breast Cancer Survivors
officialTitle: Enhancing Exercise in Breast Cancer Survivors
primaryOutcomeMeasure: change in number of minutes of moderate to strenuous physical activity
eligibilityCriteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* no health restrictions on performing moderate to strenuous physical activity
* must be 18 years or older and able to give legal consent

Exclusion Criteria:

* may not be participating in another research study regarding exercise
* restrictions on performing physical activity
